          <h3>Garage That Behaves</h3>
          <p class="meta">Tilt sensor + relay + safety close</p>
          <p>Auto‑close at night, alerts if open, one‑tap close from the car.</p>
          <div class="combo"><strong>Best combo:</strong> ZEN16/17 relay, ZSE43 tilt, safety delay + buzzer light scene on Z‑Box.</div>
        </article>

        <article class="card" data-tags="safety">
          <h3>Whole‑Home Fire Alerts</h3>
