        <article class="card">
          <h3>Leak Kit + Auto Shutoff</h3>
          <p>Starter safety: two leak sensors + Titan on the main. Text and email alerts.</p>
          <div class="combo"><strong>Best combo:</strong> Z‑Box + ZSE42 x2 + ZAC36 Titan.</div>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Smart Lock + Welcome Scene</h3>
          <p>Unlock → foyer lights on, thermostat comfy. Great for condos and townhomes.</p>
